    {
      "name": "Sharky Eats Puffies",
      "description": "Mualani regenerates 8 Energy when obtaining a Puffer. You must first unlock the Ascension Talent \"Heat-Resistant Freshwater Floater.\"\nAdditionally, Boomsharka-laka deals 75% increased DMG.",
      "icon": "https://gi.yatta.moe/assets/UI/UI_Talent_S_Mualani_03.png"
    },
    {
      "name": "Same Style of Surfboard on Sale!",
